Created with the ARTIST 16 2nd 🔥

I proudly present you my very first image created with the XP pen on the big Artist 16 pen display! Thanks a lot to @xppen_de for sending me the great looking LE PETIT PRINCE EDITION. It’s a pleasure to work with your stuff! 

The unboxing was a great experience too - nice merch in le petit prince style and really useful tools! Also the gloves are well designed! the preparation was really easy (also for a beginner) and it was possible to start working immediately. 

The whole working-process was a great creative trip! I’ve never used such a big display to creat my art and it was (and still is) an amazing experience! The pen works so smooth and it feels so comfortable to use it for my art. I’m 100% sure that I’ll continue working with the Artist 16 2nd and I can’t wait to start working on the next piece! 

If you’re interested in this stuff you should check out this: 

https://bit.ly/3MlavvF

 and (of course) the Insta-Profiles of @xppen & @xppen_de 🔥

Have a peaceful day! 

Bob

.
.
.
